choices.text:
Put together a healthy meal plan for me for seven days.  My restrictions are dairy, milk-based yogurt, garlic, honey, almonds, almond butter, pistachios, and cashews
Here is your seven day menu:
Day 1: Grilled Chicken Salad (Roma tomatoes, mozzarella cheese)
Day 2-3: Vegetable Curry with Paneer (Indian spices, vegetables)
Day 4-5: Falaf, Feta Cheese and Hummus (Chickpeas, feta cheese, hummus)
Day 6-7: Lentil Soup with Quinoa (Lentils, quinoa)
